				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hi Oleg,
<br />

<br />
Wow, you know your stuff!
<br />

<br />
I had the <span style="font-weight: bold">tc_hook_register();</span> before the end brackets:
<br />

<br />
			</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$error = TRUE;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$error_msg .= &#40; &#40; isset&#40;$error_msg&#41; &#41; ? '&lt;br /&gt;' &#58; '' &#41; . &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$lang&#91;'Fields_empty'&#93;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;tc_hook_register&#40;&#41;;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />
	
<br />
Instead of after:
<br />

<br />
			</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">$error = TRUE;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$error_msg .= &#40; &#40; isset&#40;$error_msg&#41; &#41; ? '&lt;br /&gt;' &#58; '' &#41; . &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;$lang&#91;'Fields_empty'&#93;;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;&#125;
<br />
&nbsp; &nbsp;tc_hook_register&#40;&#41;;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
I fixed it and it works like a charm!
<br />

<br />
Great MOD, great support, great guy!
<br />

<br />
Keep it up!
<br />

<br />
Thanks,
<br />
Andres</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
